article.headline: Griffin, Kot lead Wyoming past San Jose State 80-75
article.description: — Sam Griffin had 21 points, Akuel Kot scored 20 and Wyoming defeated San Jose State 80-75 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Griffin, Kot lead Wyoming past San Jose State 80-75
article.story: SAN JOSE, Calif. -- — Sam Griffin had 21 points, Akuel Kot scored 20 and Wyoming defeated San Jose State 80-75 on Saturday night. Griffin also added seven rebounds for the Cowboys (13-12, 6-6 Mountain West Conference). Kot hit four 3-pointers and grabbed five rebounds. Mason Walters scored 18 on 7-for-12 shooting. Latrell Davis finished with 20 points for the Spartans (9-17, 2-11). Myron Amey Jr. added 19 points, six assists and four steals. Tibet Gorener also had nine points. Wyoming went into halftime leading San Jose State 43-29. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
